title: Russia's Lavrov says Washington declines deeper military talks on Syria
text:
14 Russia's Lavrov says Washington declines deeper military talks on Syria 
Reuters: Russian Foreign Minister Sergei Lavrov said the United States declined to send a high-level military delegation to Moscow to discuss deeper coordination in fighting in Syria as had been proposed by Moscow.Lavrov said the proposal was made by Russian President Vladimir Putin during his visit to New York in late September.
